[[File:SmugglersCanyon-SotE.png|250px|thumb|Smuggler's Canyon]]
'''Smuggler's Canyon''', also known as '''Smuggler's Gorge''', was a canyon on the [[Moon/Legends|moon]] [[Gall/Legends|Gall]], located within the [[Grand Trench]] canyons.

The canyon consisted of steep slopes and high cliffs and walls. An [[Cadavine Sector Fleet Imperial Enclave|Imperial Enclave]] was stationed at this barren location. Despite the scarcity of vegetation and life, a sub-species of [[Wampa/Legends|wampa]], called the [[cliff wampa]], lived there.

Dash Rendar visited Smuggler's Canyon on his quest to find [[Boba Fett/Legends|Boba Fett]] and his cargo of [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] frozen in [[Carbonite/Legends|carbonite]]. He eventually found Fett and defeated him in an air duel, damaging his ship, [[Slave I/Legends|''Slave I'']], before Fett escaped.

